data.name: Halo World Championship 2022
data.description: The last event of the season will crown your 2022 Halo World Champions! Join us in Seattle or tune in live to catch all of the action. Follow @HCS to stay up to date on details.

venue.name: Seattle Convention Center - The Arch (Halls D, E, F)

tournaments.name: Halo World Championship 2022 FFA
tournaments.description: The 2022 Halo World Championship FFA will be a moment to remember! Test your skills against the best Halo Infinite players in the world!

tournaments.name: Halo World Championship 2022 4v4
tournaments.description: After a competitive first year of Halo Infinite esports, who will ultimately sit on top of the throne? Check back here for updated brackets and keep tabs on all of your favorite teams!
